msgstr "得益于 Qute，Quarkus 还让 MVC 架构的实现变得非常简单。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/web.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Associated with the https://docs.quarkiverse.io/quarkus-web-bundler/dev/[Web Bundler extension], the road is open to build modern web applications for all your needs."
msgstr "借助 link:https://docs.quarkiverse.io/quarkus-web-bundler/dev/[Web Bundler 扩展] ，您将能够开发满足各种需求的现代 Web 应用程序。"

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/main/guides/web.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "src/main/java/rest/Todos.java"
